profile: Trueline Moulding and Rise & Run create premium interior stairs, railings, mouldings and complementary products and services for builders, developers, designers, and homeowners. Our outstanding personal service and commitment to excellence has made Rise & Run the first choice among builders and homeowners across the Okanagan Valley for nearly two decades. With Rise & Run now a division of Trueline Moulding, we can offer more to our customers. Our ongoing dedication to our customers allows us to meet and exceed expectations. If you are looking for a focal point, visual impact, or a piece of artwork in your home then our company is here to help you create one and make your vision come true.
